### GET /api/v1/admin/tariffs/fare/quote
### Descripción: Cotizar tarifa (desde contexto admin). Requiere Admin/Support + X-Tenant-Id.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, X-Tenant-Id: <guid>
### Query: distanceKm, durationMin
### Códigos: 200 OK (QuoteFareDto) | 404 NO_ACTIVE_TARIFF | 400

# @name quoteFareAdmin
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tariffs/fare/quote?distanceKm=5.0&durationMin=15
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "fareAmount": 12.50,
#   "currency": "USD",
#   "tariffPlanId": "guid"
# }

### Response error (404): NO_ACTIVE_TARIFF / NO_APPLICABLE_TARIFF
